            <title>[FLINK-5160] SecurityContextTest#testCreateInsecureHadoopCtx fails on windows</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-5160</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The test uses the wrong method to retrieve the current user name when run on Windows.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Windows 10&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
