                            <comment id="15702253" author="githubbot" created="Mon, 28 Nov 2016 15:38:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user zentol opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/2888&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/2888&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-5160&quot; title=&quot;SecurityContextTest#testCreateInsecureHadoopCtx fails on windows&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-5160&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-5160&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Fix SecurityContextTest#testCreateInsecureHadoopCt on Wi&#8230;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    This PR resolves in issue in the SecurityUtilsTest class, which tries to call `getUserName()` on `com.sun.security.auth.module.NTSystem`. However, as documented &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;here&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/jre/api/security/jaas/spec/com/sun/security/auth/module/NTSystem.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/jre/api/security/jaas/spec/com/sun/security/auth/module/NTSystem.html&lt;/a&gt;) this method does not exist; on Windows it is called `getName()`.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can merge this pull request into a Git repository by running:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    $ git pull &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/zentol/flink&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/zentol/flink&lt;/a&gt; 5160_test_hadoop&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Alternatively you can review and apply these changes as the patch at:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/2888.patch&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/2888.patch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

